            <h3>Q: Which court handles North Bay family law cases?</h3>
            <p>A: Cases are heard at the Superior Court of Justice — North Bay Courthouse, 360 Plouffe Street, North Bay. Miao He attends in person when required. Full Mandarin service, Zoom available. Call 647-930-6688.</p>
